\n  File \"/usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/requests/sessions.py\", line 589, in request\n    resp = self.send(prep, **send_kwargs)\n\n  File \"/usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/requests/sessions.py\", line 703, in send\n    r = adapter.send(request, **kwargs)\n\n  File \"/usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages/huggingface_hub/utils/_http.py\", line 104, in send\n    raise OfflineModeIsEnabled(\n\nhuggingface_hub.errors.OfflineModeIsEnabled: Cannot reach https://huggingface.co/api/models/meta-llama/Meta-Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct/tree/main?recursive=True&expand=False: offline mode is enabled. To disable it, please unset the `HF_HUB_OFFLINE` environment variable.\n rank=0\nError: ShardCannotStart\n2025-04-24T18:48:01.819511Z ERROR text_generation_launcher: Shard 0 failed to start\n2025-04-24T18:48:01.819543Z  INFO text_generation_launcher: Shutting down shards\n```\n\n### Information\n\n- [x] Docker\n- [ ] The CLI directly\n\n### Tasks\n\n- [x] An officially supported command\n- [ ] My own modifications\n\n### Reproduction\n\nRun TGI with `HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1` env var:\n\n```\ndocker run -p 8080:80 \\\n   --runtime=habana \\\n   --cap-add=sys_nice \\\n   --ipc=host \\\n   -v $volume:/data \\\n   -e HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1 \\\n   -e MAX_TOTAL_TOKENS=2048 \\\n   -e PREFILL_BATCH_BUCKET_SIZE=2 \\\n   -e BATCH_BUCKET_SIZE=32 \\\n   -e PAD_SEQUENCE_TO_MULTIPLE_OF=256 \\\n   ghcr.io/huggingface/text-generation-inference:3.2.3-gaudi \\\n   --model-id $model \\\n   --max-input-tokens 1024 \\\n   --max-total-tokens 2048 \\\n   --max-batch-prefill-tokens 2048 \\\n   --max-batch-size 32 \\\n   --max-waiting-tokens 7 \\\n   --waiting-served-ratio 1.2 \\\n   --max-concurrent-requests 64\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nTGI-gaudi should be able to gracefully handle offline mode when the `model_id` is provided, findable, and mounted to the running container. This would reach parity with how other TGI backends work.\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/huggingface/text-generation-inference/commit/e3b3eecc96d2d7bbca2a6e909a724f341ebf584e", "https://github.com/huggingface/text-generation-inference/commit/790a3b5ed28fa7429179514450ee8eb067e4d16e", "https://github.com/huggingface/text-generation-inference/commit/3e9f5ba159ec7f0ca34832c2df88e95eb785ffd5"], "created_at": "2025-04-25T12:57:51Z"}
